   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Paid to Zoilos, son of Maron, and the remaining weavers of the village of Philadelphia by Nomisianos, slave of Nemesianus, 12 dr(acmas). (2nd hand) Likewise for the month Pauni another 8 dr(achmas)."</ab>
